Device Migration Table
----------------------
- Applicable only in processes where the new device has been implemented. 
This device transition is recommended to take advantage of additional
capabilities and improved modeling.
- If only the "old" device(s) exist in a particular technology, please 
continue to use them.
- Jazz will be updating design kits with the newer devices.
                          
