pdiode         pdiode_3t
p3p3diode      p3p3diode_3t


Summary of Devices Changes
--------------------------
Capacitors:
The two terminal capacitors over well are no longer supported, but still
included in the design kit for legacy purposes.  Customers should begin
using their 4 terminal counterparts.  These new devices offer the ability
to specify values for the substrate and well connections.

Diodes:
The two terminal p-type diodes are no longer supported, but still 
included in the design kit for legacy purposes.  Customers should begin
using their 3 terminal counterparts.  To take into account the p-type
substrate, these new devices contain a p-type diode with an nwell diode.
